{"tid":2171724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手推】有線體育記者用「歐聯決賽」報道 為近日解雇開台元老事件發聲！！","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T15:23:04.000Z","uid":147837,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8d81cbfcb1349563bcf07b66d967ea2623e88db1","tid":2171724,"uid":147837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/08/24/143147_9d0f00c4abf3186cd769a0df0d6e1894.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F24%2F143147_9d0f00c4abf3186cd769a0df0d6e1894.jpeg&h=cac78a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1537780556414007/?vh=e&amp;extid=FBzk1023kVB1odvN&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1537780556414007%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DFBzk1023kVB1odvN%26d%3Dn&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzslQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=c5fc883e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1537780556414007/?vh=e&amp;extid=FBzk1023kVB1odvN&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">獎盃背後，包含了多少人的付出呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n首度來到歐聯決賽的聖日耳門，有麥巴比傳送，尼馬起腳，但紐亞亦都身手非凡。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">士氣總不可以輸的，團隊精神何時都重要。</span><br />\n<br />\n今屆歐聯只要有利雲度夫斯基上陣，他每場都有入球的神話，成為過去，這球中柱。<br />\n<br />\n何解啊、何解啊，或者迪馬利亞都想問問原因，<span class=\"red\">為何美好的一切，竟然沒有好好珍惜，又令多少人感到惋惜呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n由分組賽去到四強，拜仁十戰全勝，入了42球，往績有目共睹，<span class=\"red\">建立從來並不容易，但摧毀可以只是轉眼之間。</span><br />\n<br />\n艾拿巴<span class=\"red\">這樣誤傳，有如自毀長城</span>，只是麥巴比最後射得太正。<br />\n<br />\n換邊之後，當基拿比粗野地弄跌了尼馬，就引發一段插曲。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">大家都是斯文人啊，要彬彬有禮才是嘛</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">打茅波就不好的</span>，拜仁來展示技術，京士利高文可以頭槌寫下珍貴的一頁，都要有賴甘美治精準的傳送才行的，59分鐘出現全場唯一入球。<br />\n<br />\n踢波環環相扣，拜仁防線就有紐亞做最強後盾。<br />\n<br />\n聖日耳門最終都無法扭轉敗局，拜仁第六度成為歐洲盟主。<br />\n<br />\n歐聯、德甲加上德國盃，他們是今季的三冠王。<br />\n<br />\n疫情之下，閉門的決賽或者<span class=\"red\">難免氣氛不同，但有一眾隊員並肩而行，依然並不孤單。</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n事件懶人包（引用SKW站長 巴打個Post）：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169413</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懶人包整合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/08/24/144529_63ddf2b3d71d3728bf24890c5012d6d6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F24%2F144529_63ddf2b3d71d3728bf24890c5012d6d6.jpeg&h=45be6d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實名聯署名單我照舊唔想擺上嚟，你可以自己搵<br />\n<br />\n有線炒咗三個工程高層，點解係大件事：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/有線新聞炒三個工程高層-點解要咁大反應/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%82%92%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E5%92%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzslQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=ee83a951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%82%92%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E8%A6%81%E5%92%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%2F&h=3febc03e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/有線新聞炒三個工程高層-點解要咁大反應/</a><br />\n<br />\n工程師對新聞部有幾咁重要，可以睇睇呢度：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/627241359/posts/10157194523281360/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F627241359%2Fposts%2F10157194523281360%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzslQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=0110e4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/627241359/posts/10157194523281360/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d402e9de2e41aabc5573180738